#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.melt.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.melt"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt:1 of
msgid ""
"Unpivot a DataFrame from wide to long format, optionally leaving "
"identifiers set."
msgstr "将 DataFrame 从宽格式转换为长格式，可选择保留标识符。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt:3 of
msgid ""
"This function is useful to massage a DataFrame into a format where one or"
" more columns are identifier variables (`id_vars`), while all other "
"columns, considered measured variables (`value_vars`), are \"unpivoted\" "
"to the row axis, leaving just two non-identifier columns, 'variable' and "
"'value'."
msgstr ""
"此函数用于将 DataFrame 调整为一种格式，其中一列或多列为标识变量（`id_vars"
"`），而所有其他列（视为测量变量 `value_vars`）则被“展开”到行轴上，最终"
"仅保留两个非标识列：'variable' 和 'value'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt:9 of
msgid "Column(s) to use as identifier variables."
msgstr "用作标识变量的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt:11 of
msgid ""
"Column(s) to unpivot. If not specified, uses all columns that are not set"
" as `id_vars`."
msgstr "要展开的列。如果未指定，则使用所有未设置为 `id_vars` 的列。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt:14 of
msgid ""
"Name to use for the 'variable' column. If None it uses "
"``frame.columns.name`` or 'variable'."
msgstr ""
"用于 'variable' 列的名称。如果为 None，则使用 ``frame.columns.name`` 或 '"
"variable'。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt:17 of
msgid "Name to use for the 'value' column."
msgstr "用于 'value' 列的名称。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt:19 of
msgid "If columns are a MultiIndex then use this level to melt."
msgstr "如果列是 MultiIndex，则使用此层级进行展开。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt:21 of
msgid ""
"If True, original index is ignored. If False, the original index is "
"retained. Index labels will be repeated as necessary."
msgstr ""
"如果为 True，则忽略原始索引；如果为 False，则保留原始索引。索引标签将根据"
"需要重复。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt:25 of
msgid "Unpivoted DataFrame."
msgstr "展开后的 DataFrame。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.reshape.melt.melt:28 of
msgid ""
":py:obj:`melt`, :py:obj:`pivot_table`, :py:obj:`DataFrame.pivot`, "
":py:obj:`Series.explode`"
msgstr ""

